Package cvoigt.gropro2020.Generator

Interface IGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaGenerator, LCG, PolarGenerator, SinusGenerator
    public interface IGenerator
    This Interface provides a standardized de.cae.Generator that all Generators need to Implement.

    The de.cae.Generator needs to have functions for: - Generate new random Value - Range of Values - Generate a List of random Values

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Cevin Voigt
